creator: Art Filters & Photo effects
descriptionHtml:
Discover your artistic potential with Art filters!
This user-friendly and multifunctional photo editor makes you an artist by creating diverse pencil sketches of your photos!

Select a picture from your gallery or take one with camera to create a sketch of any type with just one button click.

Art Filters provides a number of filters that add your photos fresh and creative touches! To get your lovely handmade drawings and paintings with perfect edges and curves, pick any filter effect which find suitable. Regarding its type, a filter creates accurate contour sketch, watercolor, cartoon or many other art styles. Such type of photo makes your posts attention-grabbing on social sites.

Art filters features:

1. More then 200+ wonderful filters in Art filters
2. Turn photo to Cartoon, Pencil Sketch, Watercolor painting and Oil Art Painting effects
3. Perfect HD selfie
4. Automatic Image Background remove
5. Automatic background removal, very easy to change the background of an image with one click
6. Photo adjustment tool: contrast, saturation, brightness, shadows, temperature and sharpness
7. Crop photo and more

The app is an all-in-one illustration tool and photo maker. The best and easiest way to own personal works of art and express your creativity to the world.

With the help of this app, house designs can be created, decorated or changed. Plus, the art effects are perfectly suitable to make such works of art like the paintings by Leonardo da Vinci. Each of the effects has its own style, atmosphere, mood and unique feature.
To possess the picture you want, please, take into consideration quality of photos and effects.

All art effects, photo sketch and art filters operate online, so you need network connection while using the app.

We are daily update our art effects, art filters and photo sketches

Save your works with a single touch of button. Sharing your photo on social media like Facebook, Twitter, E-mail, Message, etc. is also available.

Please Note: all the images made with this app are saved inside "Deep Art Picture" folder on your device.
descriptionShort: Turn photo into art, sketch art, pop art, watercolor and more photo effects

creator: Art Filters & Photo effects
descriptionHtml:
Discover your artistic potential with Art filters!
This user-friendly and multifunctional photo editor makes you an artist by creating diverse pencil sketches of your photos!

Select a picture from your gallery or take one with camera to create a sketch of any type with just one button click.

Art Filters provides a number of filters that add your photos fresh and creative touches! To get your lovely handmade drawings and paintings with perfect edges and curves, pick any filter effect which find suitable. Regarding its type, a filter creates accurate contour sketch, watercolor, cartoon or many other art styles. Such type of photo makes your posts attention-grabbing on social sites.

Art filters features:

1. More then 200+ wonderful filters in Art filters
2. Turn photo to Cartoon, Pencil Sketch, Watercolor painting and Oil Art Painting effects
3. Perfect HD selfie
4. Automatic Image Background remove
5. Automatic background removal, very easy to change the background of an image with one click
6. Photo adjustment tool: contrast, saturation, brightness, shadows, temperature and sharpness
7. Crop photo and more

The app is an all-in-one illustration tool and photo maker. The best and easiest way to own personal works of art and express your creativity to the world.

With the help of this app, house designs can be created, decorated or changed. Plus, the art effects are perfectly suitable to make such works of art like the paintings by Leonardo da Vinci. Each of the effects has its own style, atmosphere, mood and unique feature.
To possess the picture you want, please, take into consideration quality of photos and effects.

All art effects, photo sketch and art filters operate online, so you need network connection while using the app.

We are daily update our art effects, art filters and photo sketches

Save your works with a single touch of button. Sharing your photo on social media like Facebook, Twitter, E-mail, Message, etc. is also available.

Please Note: all the images made with this app are saved inside "Deep Art Picture" folder on your device.

Art Filters Photo Editor is user-friendly which can add artistic effects, like pop-art, oil painting and cartoon to your pictures, apply art filters, give sketch effects and prism effect.

HOW TO USE?

Just select the photo from your gallery or take a snap from the camera to create a stylish glamour blending filter effect with just one button click.
Now turn your mobile phone gallery into an art gallery with the art filters inspired by famous artists.

KEY HIGHLIGHTS

- Art Filters provides various unique filters consisting of art filters, artists, cartoon effects, sketch styles, proudly presented to you by artists, painters, cartoonists, photographers and art enthusiasts. This makes your photos posts an attention-grabbing on social platforms to get more engagements.

- Consider the quality of photos to get the best outcome from the filters and effects that can balance the right amount of contrast, saturation, brightness, shadows, temperature and sharpness. Turn your pictures into filters, drawing and much more with perfect edges and curves just like the handmade artwork.

- You can also use this app for house design creation, decoration and changes as needed. Each effect has its own style, atmosphere, mood and unique features.

ART FILTER FEATURES:

1. More than 200+ wonderful filters in Art filters
2. Turn photo to Cartoon, Pencil Sketch, Watercolor painting and Oil Art Painting effects
3. Perfect HD selfie
4. Automatic Image Background remove
5. Automatic background removal, very easy to change the background of an image with one click
6. Photo adjustment tool: contrast, saturation, brightness, shadows, temperature and sharpness
7. Crop photo and more

The app is an all-in-one illustration tool and photo maker. Now expressing your creativity to the world is easy and at your fingertips.

Please Note :

- All art effects, photo sketches and art filters operate online, so you need network connection while using the app.

- We update new effects, art filters, and photo sketches on a daily basis. Make sure you have the latest version of the app.

- Save your masterpiece with a single touch of a button. Share your artwork on social media like Facebook, Twitter, E-mail, Message, etc is also available.

- All the images made with this app are saved inside the ""Deep Art Picture"" folder on your device.

Follow us on:
Facebook https://www.facebook.com/artfiltersai/
Instagram https://www.instagram.com/artfiltersai/
Twitter https://www.twitter.com/artfiltersai/

If you have any feedback, feel free to drop it here in the comments.

Art Filters Photo Editor is user-friendly which can add artistic effects, like pop-art, oil painting and cartoon to your pictures, apply art filters, give sketch effects and prism effect.

HOW TO USE?

Just select the photo from your gallery or take a snap from the camera to create a stylish glamour blending filter effect with just one button click.
Now turn your mobile phone gallery into an art gallery with the art filters inspired by famous artists.

KEY HIGHLIGHTS

- Art Filters provides various unique filters consisting of art filters, artists, cartoon effects, sketch styles, proudly presented to you by artists, painters, cartoonists, photographers and art enthusiasts. This makes your photos posts an attention-grabbing on social platforms to get more engagements.

- Consider the quality of photos to get the best outcome from the filters and effects that can balance the right amount of contrast, saturation, brightness, shadows, temperature and sharpness. Turn your pictures into filters, drawing and much more with perfect edges and curves just like the handmade artwork.

- You can also use this app for house design creation, decoration and changes as needed. Each effect has its own style, atmosphere, mood and unique features.

ART FILTER FEATURES:

1. More than 200+ wonderful filters in Art filters
2. Turn photo to Cartoon, Pencil Sketch, Watercolor painting and Oil Art Painting effects
3. Perfect HD selfie
4. Automatic Image Background remove
5. Automatic background removal, very easy to change the background of an image with one click
6. Photo adjustment tool: contrast, saturation, brightness, shadows, temperature and sharpness
7. Crop photo and more

The app is an all-in-one illustration tool and photo maker. Now expressing your creativity to the world is easy and at your fingertips.

Please Note :

- All art effects, photo sketches and art filters operate online, so you need network connection while using the app.

- We update new effects, art filters, and photo sketches on a daily basis. Make sure you have the latest version of the app.

- Save your masterpiece with a single touch of a button. Share your artwork on social media like Facebook, Twitter, E-mail, Message, etc is also available.

- All the images made with this app are saved inside the ""Deep Art Picture"" folder on your device.

Follow us on:
Facebook https://www.facebook.com/artfiltersai/
Instagram https://www.instagram.com/artfiltersai/
Twitter https://www.twitter.com/artfiltersai/

If you have any feedback, feel free to drop it here in the comments.
